SPARK DEPENDENCIES CONF:
	1. Go to Spark API and select current maven dependencies
	2. Click pom.xml->select pom.xml->pass chosen dependency at the bottom of the file
	3. Right click on project->configure->Scala nature
	4. Right click on Scala library container -> properties -> select 2.11.11
	5. Right click on project -> Select Java Build Path -> Select Source -> Add Folder -> Select main -> Click Create new -> Click next -> Add -> finish
	6.
	 
